INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2012-04-26 11:21:04','2012-04-26 01:21:04','<h2>What is it?</h2>\r\nThis module is a phone book application based on top of Drupal. It imports phone book entries from a separate csv file to Drupal as Nodes and provides a user interface for user to search phone list entries.\r\n<h2>Challenges</h2>\r\n<h3>Scalability</h3>\r\nApplication needs to handle large set of data import without reaching memory limit and should be restricted in a reasonable time.\r\nI\'ve optimized the query to minimize insertion time and broken down the import process to fragments for better memory utilization.\r\n<h3>Dirty data cleansing</h3>\r\nApplication need to be robust enough to handle dirty data as well as mal-formatted input file.\r\nThe import process should not be interrupted and notice and log information should be provided to user for any error encountered in the whole import process.\r\n<h3>Ajax experience</h3>\r\nApplication needs to be Ajax based for better usability.','Phone list module for TfNSW v1.0 - Drupal module development','','publish','open','open','','phone-list-drupal-module-1-0','','','2012-04-27 14:01:03','2012-04-27 04:01:03','',0,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/?p=1',0,'post','',0),(2,1,'2010-12-17 02:21:04','2010-12-16 15:21:04','','Home','','publish','open','closed','','home','','','2014-04-25 12:00:50','2014-04-25 02:00:50','',0,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2010-12-19 09:41:53','2010-12-19 09:41:53','This is the content of the home page','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave','','','2010-12-19 09:41:53','2010-12-19 09:41:53','',2,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/?p=5',0,'revision','',0),(158,1,'2011-04-09 21:37:03','2011-04-09 11:37:03','Helps Life Style Medicine to rebuild their website using <a href=\"http://symfony.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Symfony </a>framework.\r\n\r\nThis project also involves content migration from old website to <a href=\"http://symfony.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Symfony</a