2012-04-26 11:11:09','2012-04-26 01:11:09','',1,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/1-revision-8',0,'revision','',0),(572,1,'2012-04-27 10:24:17','2012-04-27 00:24:17','','drupal-logo','','inherit','open','open','','drupal-logo','','','2012-04-27 10:24:17','2012-04-27 00:24:17','',0,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/drupal-logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(573,1,'2012-04-27 10:24:17','2012-04-27 00:24:17','<h2>What is it?</h2>\r\nThis module is a phone book application based on top of Drupal. It imports phone book entries from a separate csv file to Drupal as Nodes and provides a user interface for user to search phone list entries.\r\n<h2>Challenges</h2>\r\n<h3>Scalability</h3>\r\nApplication needs to handle large set of data import without reaching memory limit and should be restricted in a reasonable time.\r\nI\'ve optimized the query to minimize insertion time and broken down the import process to fragments for better memory utilization.\r\n\r\n* Dirty data cleansing - application need to be robust enough to handle dirty data as well as mal-formatted input file.\r\nThe import process should not be interrupted and notice and log information should be provided to user for any error encountered in the whole import process.\r\n\r\n* Ajax experience - application needs to be Ajax based to better usability.','Phone list module for TfNSW v1.0 - Drupal module development','','inherit','open','open','','1-revision-9','','','2012-04-27 10:24:17','2012-04-27 00:24:17','',1,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/1-revision-9',0,'revision','',0),(574,1,'2012-04-27 10:24:50','2012-04-27 00:24:50','<h2>What is it?</h2>\r\nThis module is a phone book application based on top of Drupal. It imports phone book entries from a separate csv file to Drupal as Nodes and provides a user interface for user to search phone list entries.\r\n<h2>Challenges</h2>\r\n<h3>Scalability</h3>\r\nApplication needs to handle large set of data import without reaching memory limit and should be restricted in a reasonable time.\r\nI\'ve optimized the query to minimize insertion time and broken down the import process to fragments for better memory utilization.\r\n<h3>Dirty data cleansing</h3>\r\nApplication need to be robust enough to handle dirty data as well as mal-formatted input file.\r\nThe import process should not be interrupted and notice and log information should be provided to user for any error encountered in the whole import process.\r\n<h3>Ajax experience</h3>\r\nApplication needs to be Ajax based to better usability.','Phone list module for TfNSW v1.0 - Drupal module development','','inherit','open','open','','1-revision-10','','','2012-04-27 10:24:50','2012-04-27 00:24:50','',1,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/1-revision-10',0,'revision','',0),(575,1,'2014-07-08 13:39:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Phone list module v2.0 is a rewrite of the <a title=\"Phone list module for TfNSW v1.0 â€“ Drupal module development\" href=\"http://www.jeffreycai.com/phone-list-drupal-module-1-0\">version 1.0</a>.\n\nThere is mi','Phone list module for TfNSW v2.0 â€“ Drupal module development','','draft','open','open','','phone-list-drupal-module-2-0','','','2014-07-08 13:39:23','2014-07-08 03:39:23','',0,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/?p=575',0,'post','',0),(576,1,'2012-04-27 14:29:20','2012-04-27 04:29:20','Phone list module v2.0 is a rewrite of the <a title=\"Phone list module for TfNSW v1.0 â€“ Drupal module development\" href=\"http://www.jeffreycai.com/phone-list-drupal-module-1-0\">version 1.0</a>.\n\nThere is mi','Phone list module for TfNSW v2.0 â€“ Drupal module development','','inherit','open','open','','575-revision','','','2012-04-27 14:29:20','2012-04-27 04:29:20','',575,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/575-revision',0,'revision','',0),(577,1,'2011-05-19 22:21:29','2011-05-19 12:21:29','','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-13','','','2011-05-19 22:21:29','2011-05-19 12:21:29','',2,'http://www.jeffreycai.com/2-revision-13',0,'revision','',0),(578,1,'2012-